CustomField.description: This is the calculated end date for the project. It is the earlier of the end date of the earliest task and the desired end date of the project
CustomField.formula: IF(ISBLANK(project_cloud__End__c), project_cloud__Autonomous_End__c, IF(project_cloud__Autonomous_End__c > project_cloud__End__c, project_cloud__Autonomous_End__c, project_cloud__End__c))
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The calculated end date of the Project, derived from the Desired End Date and the Calculated End Date of the latest Project Task.
CustomField.label: Calculated End Date
